{"tid":1472473,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［拆局］我有辦法攪革命同時不流血、場面仲好好睇！上國際頭條！！！爭取民意同時又唔暴力","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T16:26:38.000Z","uid":188828,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9d13f9fd79a89ba477a489e93521ed0af80171","tid":1472473,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"就係著住毛毛公仔衫去衝擊警方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDhS2H1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDhS2H1.png&h=a8deaf16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家只識嗌「光復香港 時代革命」但根本未準備好攪革命 咩係革命？會流血會有混亂 你攪遊行要唔要道歉啊？你攪到遊客係香港觀光行程 你攪到店舖早閂門冇得購物 你攪遊擊要唔要道歉啊？你攪到遊客落一落街都食彈 吸催淚煙 你攪全民三罷又要唔要道歉啊？你攪到遊客要改路 改行程 餐廳都未必開 呢啲又唔見你地爭住出黎道歉？你咬斷警察手指又唔同警察道歉？你攪到佢地日日ot有精神壓力又唔道歉？佢地嗰啲民意又唔見你話重要？<br />\n<br />\n我地呢次公民抗爭就係要承認自己挑戰緊法例 承認自己唔係可愛既示威者 如果你覺得遊客無辜既 就更加要令外國對香港發旅遊警示 佢地千奇唔好黎 廢事無辜地中彈 我話你知 我同過好多外國人傾香港呢次事件 佢地好多本身已經知咩事 係覺得慘 但我地想點？知道又如何？有個美國佬直情同我講 你地用遮去同警察鬥太可笑 如果坐係度乜都唔做想改變不如返屋企 你出得黎就要預咗流血 因為革命冇不流血 呢個係殘酷既事實但我地要明白 外國人冇義務幫我地 如果我地阻到佢地上機 佢地會搵自己國家領事館 好似泰國會自己派機接遊客 迫使佢地對香港發旅遊警示先係真正焦土同攬抄 <br />\n<br />\n如果仲要介意光環同示威者形象 覺得可以幫到骨折、流血、被砍到血肉模糊、永久失明既義士手足 我建議你地可以著住毛毛公仔衫 好似迪士尼嗰啲 去遊行、圍警署、屌警察 咁樣係鏡頭下夠晒好睇掛？冇流血 冇暴力 又吸睛 仲分分中可以上國際頭條 因為我諗冇地方會攪革命既同時仲追求可愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJRc2JN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJRc2JN.png&h=2708d6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足犧牲咗咁多 你又肯犧牲幾多？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaXLDif.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaXLDif.png&h=fff80cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPUaPpX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPUaPpX.png&h=4e2e428f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPoiYim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPoiYim.png&h=3ba8ff56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01aJpYr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01aJpYr.png&h=18c7498c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eb83pYt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEb83pYt.png&h=2099ca77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0c41cf2429a1a70a3c37bcf63353828f963674b","tid":1472473,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9398a0be2167c0533980dce617ca6e8b5d16758c","tid":1472473,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e86bd0de02a813337db3bc2ee54db819ec1ae6b","tid":1472473,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22d5707899e549d0512bf8652f9a1dafbe0eae01","tid":1472473,"uid":58254,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"你試下著住出街企5分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a25084dae4da5e7f3abb53a3d4adc50a39cb398","tid":1472473,"uid":187274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"著左太空衣都冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9240a3d57492ea61afa226d59b16cbcd9c62b944","tid":1472473,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"22d5707899e549d0512bf8652f9a1dafbe0eae01","tid":1472473,"uid":58254,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"你試下著住出街企5分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"請再睇全文"},{"pid":"38146f0b300ade68577658d29d61d0ed6f98e4ab","tid":1472473,"uid":135197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22d5707899e549d0512bf8652f9a1dafbe0eae01","tid":1472473,"uid":58254,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"你試下著住出街企5分鐘<img src=\"/assets